name: Decentrawoman - Genesis - 1
description: It's a bird, its a plane, it's... a decentralized superhero for the decentralized metaverse? Introducing Decentrawoman! The hero that Decentraland didn't know it needed, but definitely deserves. In this Genesis piece, Decentrawoman soars over Genesis Plaza, her story still to be written by the citizens of Decentraland!
